These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-1::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: ice-hockey, climbing, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far right##1
3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |   3   |
| Sport   | weightlifting | climbing | ice-hockey |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-2::.
There 3 different types of food: pineapple, eggplant, grapes
1. the person eating eggplant is in an odd position##4
2. the person eating pineapple is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Food   | pineapple | grapes | eggplant |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: card-games, filmmaking, photography
1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is photography##3
3. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3       |
| Hobby   | card-games | filmmaking | photography |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-4::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: metal, disco, hip-hop
1. the fan of disco is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the fan of disco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |  3   |
| Music-Genre   | metal | hip-hop | disco |

